  <!-- EN: threepeater -->
  <Threepeater.label>三发射手</Threepeater.label>
  <!-- EN: A powerful plant that fires three peas in a burst. Slightly less accurate but faster than the peashooter. Cannot be harvested, only cut down. -->
  <Threepeater.description>强大的植物，一次发射三颗豌豆。精度略低于豌豆射手，但射速更快。无法收获，只能割除。</Threepeater.description>
  
